{"tid":115893,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益][招人] 有聲講故台 出片","createTime":"2017-02-11T02:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T10:38:50.000Z","uid":26449,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94c627e819bd6b62851f836818e5743cb074730b","tid":115893,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:30:58.000Z","msg":"第二篇第一章已經由Sab15絲打錄好了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8wmfw-9XQGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8wmfw-9XQGU&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=37603e7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8wmfw-9XQGU</a><br />\n沙士被壓 - 天黑莫回頭，背後不是人 現代篇 - 第一章：鬼壓床<br />\n作者：沙士被壓　／聲音：LIHKG@Sab15　<br />\n<br />\nYoutube頻道：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/S30lJ1 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FS30lJ1%20&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=37879445\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/S30lJ1 </a><br />\n記得要訂閱，巴絲打錄得好辛苦的，你既訂閱就係的原動力！<br />\n（頻道不會開營利，純粹分享）<br />\n<br />\n現在手上有兩個故事錄製中<br />\n１． 沙士被壓《天黑莫回頭，背後不是人》系列<br />\n２．裕賢先生《孤獨的島住了一個人》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，前幾天在講故台中開post想做一個Youtube有聲講故台，開始時我都係用SIRI聲製作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有巴打提意不如招人讀，之後就有4個熱心的巴絲打聯絡了我。感動<br />\n有兩個巴絲打，同佢地傾左幾句，大定都已經開始錄製了，還好專業好認真！連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實想問一下各位巴絲打有咩故事想聽？有無提供？<br />\n覺得有咩改善的地方？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在人手短缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果有興趣參加錄音的巴絲打可以聯絡<br />\nLINE：tellstory2017<br />\nEMAIL:tellstory2017@gmail.com[img][/img]<br />\n<br />\n大家都係在自己屋企錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p